{"body_text": "Mockups can be found here - #316 (comment)\n\n Load available filters (locales, names, etc)...\n ...from API\n Display filters in a dropdown list\n Filter dropdown can be filtered by text input\n Clicking a dropdown item (filter) enables that filter\n Typing text into the combobox and hitting 'enter' enables a text filter\n Clicking on an activated filter disables that filter\n Reset button clears all filters\n Upon selecting filter, new recipe list is fetched from API\n Loading message is displayed while loading new recipe list from API\n Cached recipe list is displayed until a new update comes in\n Tests\n\nBonus objectives:\n\n URL updates with filter config (so filter setups can be shared easily)\n \"Displaying X of Y items\" text\n\nReading material:\n\nGist: format for returned filters", "labels": [], "number": 395, "assignee": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andymikulski/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andymikulski/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andymikulski/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/andymikulski", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andymikulski/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/andymikulski", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andymikulski/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/2767162?v=4", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andymikulski/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andymikulski/received_events", "gravatar_id": "", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andymikulski/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "site_admin": false, "login": "andymikulski", "type": "User", "id": 2767162, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/andymikulski/followers"}, "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/mozilla/normandy", "closed_at": "2017-02-13T18:00:06Z", "body_html": "<p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.co